    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors not assessed are within the accepted scope exclusions for MRL 2 Class II device assessment. The relative hemolysis index criterion (RH < 1) is satisfied at the worst-case operating point. The assessment team concludes that the CFD model is credible for the stated COU and that the simulation evidence supports the regulatory submission decision.",
